      "description": "The Zillow app puts essential real estate tools and experts at your fingertips, no matter where you are in your home journey.\u2028Tour listings in 3D and envision your style in any room with virtual staging on Zillow Showcase℠ listings — and exchange messages with your shopping partner right in the app. Check your BuyAbility℠ score for an estimate of your home-buying budget based on your finances and current interest rates. Work with a local agent to find a home you love, and manage the buying process from pre-approval to closing, all in one place. Or, browse zillions of apartment listings and find your perfect place faster with real-time help from a virtual leasing assistant. Get the app to make it all possible.\n\n- Add a shopping partner in the app and use messages to keep your search organized\n- Reimagine homes in your style with virtual staging on Showcase℠ listings\n- Simplify home buying with mortgage pre-approval and closing, all in one place\n- Chat in real time with a virtual rental leasing assistant to get questions answered, schedule tours and more\n- Check out neighborhood details including restaurants, school districts and more\n- Track your Zestimate®, the industry-leading independent home valuation tool",
